programme.title: World Watch: Forbidden History Ep6
programme.desc: Dokumentari bersama Jamie Theakson yang menyiasat mitos dan lagenda menarik dari sejarah. Jamie dan pasukan penyelidik merungkai misteri yang membentuk budaya masyarakat setempat. Dalam episod kali ini, sepasukan penyelidik melakukan penyelidikan untuk merungkai tujuan dan cara pembinaan bangunan yang bercirikan pyramid. Walaupun piramid selalu dikaitkan dengan Mesir purba, namun ianya turut ditemui serata dunia dan mempunyai status yang ikonik. Antara negara yang turut mempunyai bangunan berciri piramid adalah di Bosnia.

programme.title: Bidadari: Rumah Kasih Suraya Ep1
programme.desc: Suraya Hanis, bekas peragawati, membuka Rumah Kasih Suraya menjelang ramadan. Didorong rasa tanggungjawab dan keinsafan, kisah ini bukan sahaja menggambarkan pengorbanannya untuk membantu insan memerlukan, tetapi juga menyingkap cabaran sebenar kerjaya selebriti yang sering dilihat glamor, namun penuh fitnah, godaan, dan memerlukan keimanan, ketabahan mental, serta usaha gigih untuk berjaya. Dalam episod ini tentang Suraya menyewa banglo Datuk Badar untuk membuka rumah kebajikan khas untuk golongan artis veteran. Suraya seorang supermodel dan usahawan tudung yang popular. Primadona Zaiton akan turut menghuni di Rumah Kasih Suraya. Primadona Zaiton adalah artis veteran yang sangat popular satu masa dulu dan pernah memenangi anugerah Pelakon Wanita Terbaik. Pelakon: Nad Zainal, Fauziah Ahmad Daud, Fad Anuar, Dato Jalalauddin Hassan, Nor Albaniah, Sobri Anuar, dan Adam Shahz.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Resort Kasih Bunga Raya Ep1
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kisah suka duka kehidupan sebagai pekerja resort yang muhibah. Ali, Santi dan Teong telah berjaya melepasi temuduga dan mula berkhidmat di Resort Kasih Bunga Raya. Namun kehadiran seorang tetamu yang cerewet telah menduga mereka. Hasbullah ditugaskan oleh orang atasannya untuk menjalankan sesi temuduga pengambilan kakitangan baharu. Akhirnya tiga peserta telah dipilih untuk mengisi kekosongan jawatan di resort tersebut. Pelbagai telatah mereka bertiga ketika cuba belajar perkara baru dalam tugasan harian. Deana kemudian telah berkahwin dengan Fikrie tanpa diketahui Fikrie adalah bekas teman lelaki Haryani. Suatu hari, Deana mahu menguji kesetiaan Fikrie dengan mengupah Haryani untuk jatuh cinta kepada Fikrie. Bagaimanakah kisah mereka seterusnya? Pertemuan Haryani dan Fikrie, adakah bakal membibitkan cinta lama mereka?

Ketegangan Maya membuatkan Ferdaus dan Umi tertanya-tanya. Namun Maya masih belum memiliki kekuatan untuk berterus terang tentang keadaan sebenarnya. Demi mendapatkan restu bagi mengahwini Khadeja, Dato Shikin telah menetapkan satu syarat, Ray perlu berdepan dan meminta maaf kepada kesemua 11 bekas teman wanitanya, merakam setiap kemaafan yang diberikan kepada Ray, dan menghantarnya kepada Dato' Shikin dalam tempoh 30 hari. Terdesak, Ray bersetuju dengan syarat tersebut dan meminta bantuan rakan baiknya, Kamil. Misi menjadi rumit apabila Ray dan Kamil mendapati bekas-bekas teman wanitanya, pesakit mental, jurulatih MMA, pegawai polis narkotik, barista kafe, penjaga zoo, pengusaha makanan dan pelbagai lagi, kesemuanya masih marah dengan Ray, terutamanya Aisha, kenalan rapat Ray dari bangku sekolah yang juga kononnya salah seorang dari 11 orang bekas kekasih Ray. Kali terakhir Ray bertemu dengan Aisha adalah 13 tahun lepas. Aisha menyedari bahawa Ray benar-benar telah berubah dan memutuskan untuk membantu Ray menyelesaikan misinya. Ray dan Aisha secara tidak diduga mula jatuh hati antara satu sama lain. Perasaan yang sama dirasai mereka 13 tahun lepas namun dipendam sehingga kini. Tanpa pengetahuan Ray, Dato' Shikin telah mengupah seseorang yang rapat dengan Ray untuk menggagalkan misinya. Masa 30 hari kian hampir tamat, dan Aisha merupakan orang yang terakhir dalam misi Ray untuk memohon kemaafan

programme.title: The Gadis Ep5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan ibu Shazman berjumpa dengan Lina, dia mahu Shazwan berkahwin dengan Nad dan bukan dengan Lina. Namun Nad sendiri pun tidak sukakan Shazman. Shazman datang, dia meminta maaf atas sikap ibunya. Shazman mendapat pekerjaan dan menjemput Lina dan keluarga ke rumahnya untuk majlis doa selamat. Lina meminta maaf atas perbuatannya sehingga membuat kakaknya marah. Lina minta Lisa tidak lagi berjumpa dengan Nad kerana merasakan pekerjaan yang dilakukan Nad sebagai pelaucr. Mulai saat itu Lisa merasa bersalah melihat kesungguhan kakaknya mencari wang halal untuk keluarga. Lisa nekad untuk berhenti menjadi sugar baby. Dia memberitahu Nad. Nad mengamuk. Dia perlukan Lisa untuk selesaikan hutangnya dengan Mika. Mika dan Nad bersekongkol untuk menculik Lisa ke KL agar mereka dapat selesaikan hal mereka. Di kampung, Lina risau Lisa tidak pulang-pulang. Pada suatu hari, Nasir kemalangan dan meninggal dunia tanpa sempat menyiapkan novel karangannya. Selepas kematian Nasir, Yasmin berusaha menyiapkan novel tersebut demi sebuah cinta.

programme.title: Gila Baby
programme.desc: Bob memerlukan wang yang banyak bagi membiayai kos pembedahan ayahnya di hospital. Dengan mengambil jalan mudah, Bob membantu Roy, bekas teman sekelasnya di sekolah yang selalu membulinya dahulu untuk melakukan jenayah mencuri kereta. Walaupun percubaan pertama Bob untuk aktiviti jenayah tersebut berjaya tetapi ada seorang bayi di tempat duduk belakang kereta yang dicurinya itu! Bob kini mendapati dirinya diburu oleh beberapa pihak yang tidak akan berhenti selagi Bob dan bayi tersebut tidak ditangkap! Untuk mengeruhkan lagi keadaan, dalam perjalanan menyelamatkan diri, Bob bertemu Jaja yang mengugut Bob untuk membawanya sekali kerana ingin lari dari masalahnya sendiri

programme.desc: Farah panik apabila Zahin demam panas hingga muntah-muntah. Farah mengalah dan terpaksa ambil cuti kecemasan meskipun dia baru bekerja. Kata-kata pedih daripada pengurusnya

programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep16
programme.desc: Rian terkejut apabila Afeeq menumbuk Adif, menyebabkan Adif memegang mukanya yang sakit. Adif ingin membalas tetapi Idris muncul dan menghalang pergaduhan. Idris menyuruh mereka keluar jika mahu bergaduh. Adif melihat Farhan dan kemudian beredar setelah Rian menyuruhnya pergi. Idris meminta maaf kerana mengahwinkan Rian dengan Adif dan meminta Rian mempertimbangkan keputusan masa depannya. Rian marah kerana Idris seolah-olah menyebelahi Adif. Rian beri peluang dan jumpa Adif tetapi pergaduhan berlaku sehingga Rian pengsan. Apabila esok Rian sedar dia sendiri di hotel dengan Adif tinggalkan nota supaya Rian sarapan dulu sebelum pulang. Rian terkejut, tertanya-tanya jika Rian dan Adif benar-benar tidur bersama malam tadi.

programme.title: The Gadis Ep6
programme.desc: Lisa dan Rocky masuk ke bilik Lisa, mereka menjumpai sejumlah wang dan telefon bimbit juga gambar seksi Lisa semasa bekerja sebagai sugarbaby. Tiba-tiba telefon tersebut berdering panggilan dari Dato Jefri, Lina berpura-pura menyamar sebagai Lisa bagi mendapatkan alamat tempat Lisa disembunyikan oleh Nad dan Mika. Nad terpaksa menurut kehendak Mika kerana dia mempunyai pistol dan masih berhutang dengan Mika. Mereka akan menjual Lisa kepada seorang Dato dengan harga RM70 ribu. Mika menjadi agresif apabila Lisa cuba memberitahu seorang pembersih kondo yang dia diculik. Kerana terlalu marah, Mika menumbuk Lisa dan pembersih kondo. Nad yang tidak sukakan kekasaran Mika cuba menghalangnya namun dia juga ditampar oleh Mika. Mika membawa Lisa dan Nad berpindah ke rumah lain. Di kampung, Lina dan Rocky buntu dengan cara hendak ke KL. AKhirnya Lina menghubungi Shazman dan meminta pertolongannya. Mereka bertiga ke kondo Nad. Tiba di kondo Nad, mereka nampak Nad dalam perjalanan keluar. Mereka mengepung Nad dan memaksa dia beritahu perkara sebenar.

programme.title: Terjebak Nostalgia
programme.desc: Raisa (Raisa Andriana) dan Sora (Maruli Tampubolon) menjalin hubungan cinta yang erat. Sora, seorang pianis berbakat, mendapat peluang melanjutkan pengajian muzik di Juilliard School of Music, New York. Mereka berpisah dengan janji untuk bersatu semula selepas Sora menamatkan pengajiannya. Namun, selepas dua tahun, Sora hilang tanpa jejak akibat Badai Sandy di New York. Raisa, yang sukar melupakan Sora, mula menghantar surat dalam botol ke laut dan secara ajaib menerima balasan dari New York. Dengan bantuan sahabatnya, Reza (Chicco Jerikho), Raisa pergi ke New York untuk mencari Sora. Di sana, Raisa dan Reza melalui pelbagai pengalaman yang menguji perasaan dan hubungan mereka, membawa Raisa kepada penemuan tentang cinta dan masa lalunya.

programme.title: 11 Cinta Sebelum Kamu
programme.desc: Ray, selepas melamar Khadeja, Ray bertemu bakal ibu mentuanya, Dato' Shikin, seorang ibu tunggal dan peguam terkenal. Tanpa mengetahui latar belakang keluarga Khadeja, Ray mendapati bahawa Dato' Shikin telah menyelidik kehidupan masa lalunya yang 'nakal. Demi mendapatkan restu bagi mengahwini Khadeja, Dato Shikin telah menetapkan satu syarat, Ray perlu berdepan dan meminta maaf kepada kesemua 11 bekas teman wanitanya, merakam setiap kemaafan yang diberikan kepada Ray, dan menghantarnya kepada Dato' Shikin dalam tempoh 30 hari. Terdesak, Ray bersetuju dengan syarat tersebut dan meminta bantuan rakan baiknya, Kamil. Misi menjadi rumit apabila Ray dan Kamil mendapati bekas-bekas teman wanitanya, pesakit mental, jurulatih MMA, pegawai polis narkotik, barista kafe, penjaga zoo, pengusaha makanan dan pelbagai lagi, kesemuanya masih marah dengan Ray, terutamanya Aisha, kenalan rapat Ray dari bangku sekolah yang juga kononnya salah seorang dari 11 orang bekas kekasih Ray. Kali terakhir Ray bertemu dengan Aisha adalah 13 tahun lepas. Aisha menyedari bahawa Ray benar-benar telah berubah dan memutuskan untuk membantu Ray menyelesaikan misinya. Ray dan Aisha secara tidak diduga mula jatuh hati antara satu sama lain. Perasaan yang sama dirasai mereka 13 tahun lepas namun dipendam sehingga kini. Tanpa pengetahuan Ray, Dato' Shikin telah mengupah seseorang yang rapat dengan Ray untuk menggagalkan misinya. Masa 30 hari kian hampir tamat, dan Aisha merupakan orang yang terakhir dalam misi Ray untuk memohon kemaafan

Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Love is the only Answer
programme.desc: At Bo and Cheong wedding reception, the projected was initially showing their journey of love, but suddenly a flash of a clip of Cheong and a sexy girl being intimate came up. Bo calmly ran up to the stage and announced that the wedding is cancelled. The incident rapidly became a hot topic on the internet. Within a year, back to being single again, Bo and the living life happily Cheong maintains a good relationship. One day, Cheong decided to play with love and took Bo to participate in a swinging party. The conservative Bo initially wanted to leave, but after being bribed by Cheong, she helpless and stayed. At the swinging party, the two encounter Kit and his wife Man Lai. The 4 of them develop a romantic and hot relationship... At another wedding reception, when the projector plays the groom and bride's heartwarming clips, a flash of another clip that does not want to be seen comes up...

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Polices Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: Detrimental
programme.desc: You Ji Ren is a blind man who works at a factory in an outlying island. When the factory is cut off from the outside world by a hurricane one day, a monster appears and turns whoever sees it into black shadows. As You cannot see the monster, he is able to help other coworkers leave safely and fight to kill the monster!

programme.title: Inner Senses
programme.desc: Haunted by recurring visions stemming from past traumas, Yan reaches out to psychiatrist Dr Jim to restore her sanity and overcome her troubled past. Yet, as Yan gradually heals, Jim finds himself haunted by the same disturbing images, as his suppressed memories resurface.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Moscow Mission
programme.desc: Based on the 1993 true event of the "China-Russia Train Robbery", a gang of criminals commits a heist, stealing cash and goods from the cross border train. A Chinese police officer disguises as a businessman takes charge of the operation to arrest the criminals, but uncovers a bigger conspiracy instead

programme.title: May We Chat
programme.desc: Yan, Wei Wei and Yi Ji are three troubled young women from very different backgrounds who met on We Chat, a social media platform, and will do anything to escape each of their troubled lives. When Yan suddenly disappears one day, Wei Wei and Yi Ji start to track her whereabouts, only to find out shocking truths about her that were never revealed.

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real Chosen Sleuth instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: I Believe
programme.desc: Chu Chu has been waiting for her first love for 10 years but he marries someone else in the end. As she loses faith in love, she meets a wedding planner and a handsome and rich man, who both help her get over her ex-boyfriend. As Chu Chu feels the same love from them, she must make up her mind. Who will she choose in the end?

programme.title: One More Chance
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as a down-on-his-luck gambler, Water, whose ex-girlfriend asked him to take care of their autistic son. As Water lives with his son, he soon finds his goal in life. When he discovers his sons talent in running, Water decides to give up his dissipated life and support his son to achieve his dream.

programme.title: Love For All Seasons
programme.desc: May, acting leader of the Er Mei sect, cures the incurable illness of Tiger, a rich playboy. Under the threat of her senior, May seeks help from Tiger to experience heartbreak and master the "Heartbroken Sword" style, so as to defeat her senior and preserve Er Mei sect. Will this strange and long-winding relationship reach a happy ending?

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover to a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: The Captain
programme.desc: The movie is based on a real incident of Sichuan Airlines Flight 8633 on 14 May 2018. When the cockpit windshield shatters after takeoff, the Captain manages to land the airplane safely with his level-headed swift actions and sheer determination. This is lauded as a miracle in airline history.

programme.title: I Fine… Thank You… Love You
programme.desc: Pleng, an English tutor, helps her student to pass a break up message in English to her boyfriend Gym. Gym knows nothing about English but wants to win back his girlfriend from the US, so he asks Pleng to teach him. Boorish and a slow learner, Gym makes many hilarious mistakes when learning English and ends up falling for Pleng.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Time Still Turns the Pages
programme.desc: High school teacher Cheng recalls his violent childhood memories when he finds an anonymous suicide note in the classroom. While he has to prevent the tragedy involving a suicidal student from happening, he also has to face a series of family problems with his wife wanting to divorce him and his fathers serious illness.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protg Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover to a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: As It Burns
programme.desc: Detective Wei investigates the death of Yan Zhen in an explosion which seems more than an accident to him. Wei then finds out that Yan Zhen looks a lot like Yin, the girlfriend of Yan Zhens childhood friend Lu, and uncovers a tangled web of deceit leading to surprising revelations when he merges details from the past and the present.

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 3
programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the worlds best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the worlds top detective Q got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: Chinese Odyssey 2002
programme.desc: Set in Ming Dynasty, young Emperor Zheng De escapes from the palace with his sister who disguised as a man. They run into a notorious wanderer who runs a restaurant with his boyish sister in Jiang Nan. The two pairs of siblings from vastly different social classes descend into an inescapable swirl of gender confusion, slapstick antics and love.

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: The Thundering Sword
programme.desc: Two disciples, Yu and Zheng, are sent by their master to track down the invincible weapon Thundering Sword to prevent villains from getting it. Yu encounters the daughter of a ruthless clan, Chiao, who is on her way to seek for the sword. They quickly fall for each other, but when Chiao accidentally injures Zheng, things become complicated.

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: Pursuit
programme.desc: This movie tells the tale of Lin Chong, the Sung Dynastys Chief Army Instructor who is framed by a corrupt official and has to embark on an exile fraught with danger. Helped by a monk, Lin Chong is finally able to take revenge.

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: Perils Of The Sentimental Swordsman
programme.desc: The titanic team of Director Chu Yuan and Novelist Ku Lung chose to give their hero (Ti Lung) a whole new cliffhanger-fraught adventure featuring a mysterious swordsman, a sensual swordswoman, an imperial assassin, a ghost mansion, a booby-trapped tunnel, as well as double crosses and secret missions.

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a Generals daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: Dragon Swamp
programme.desc: Fan is cheated by her lover Tong to steal her masters Jade Dragon Sword. She is jailed in the Dragon Swamp as punishment and gave birth to a pair of twins - her daughter is raised by her master, while her son is taken by Tong. Twenty years later, the sword is stolen again and Fans daughter goes seeking for it, meeting Fans friend along the way.

programme.title: Sex, Love and Hate
programme.desc: This masterpiece spins three interconnected tales about Hong Kong society's differing views on love and what women want from love. Follow a trio of Hong Kong women as they explore relationships and fulfil their hopes of finding true love.

programme.title: Iron Bodyguard
programme.desc: Wang Wu, the head of a security firm Iron Bodyguard, meets a scholar who is a member of the Reformists, a group of scholars pressing for social reform in China at the end of the Qing dynasty. The Emperor actually supports such reforms but not the Empress Dowager. She orders the Reformists to be arrested and Wang Wu gets drawn into the politics.

programme.title: Lady General Hua Mu-Lan
programme.desc: Mulan disguises herself as a male soldier to replace her aged father in a war against the barbarians. Her courage brings her victory in battles and she was promoted to a general. When Mulan returns home with glory, the chief commander asks her to marry his daughter, forcing Mulan to reveal her true identity.

programme.title: The Twin Swords
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his wife Gan Lian Zhu are the famous Twin Swords in the martial arts world. One day, they stumble upon a kidnapping plot at the Red Lotus Temple and Lian Zhu is held captive. Wu successfully escapes to find the Gan family for help, not knowing that he is sending them into an ambush by the kidnappers. Can he finally save Lian Zhu?

programme.title: Clan of Amazons
programme.desc: The martial arts world is plunged into terror when a mysterious figure known as the 'Embroidery Bandit' starts to attack convoys of precious materials. Seemingly unstoppable, the frightened clans decide to call on the expertise of Lu Xiao Feng, an inquisitive fighter and detective to capture the culprit.

programme.title: The Adulteress
programme.desc: The film is about the drugged, then disgraced wife of a peddler in the waning days of the Ching Dynasty. To make matters worse, shes soon framed for her husbands murder by her rapist, the son of the local magistrate! And even that is not the end of her woes in this emotional suspense

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wongs disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: The Dream of the Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the most widely read and filmed novel in Chinese history, this version is said to be the most successful one. Betty Lohs looks, demeanour and aura in her portrayal of Lin Dai Yu has won her the epithet "Classic Beauty".

programme.title: The Battle Wizard
programme.desc: Dali Prince Tuan Yu knows nothing about martial arts, but leaves the palace for the martial arts world. He meets a snake sorceress and his mysterious half-sister. Through various misadventures, Tuan Yu gains invincible power by sucking the cobras blood and swallowing the magic toad, eventually defeating his fathers old rival.

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Muis embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love

programme.title: The Golden Buddha
programme.desc: A map indicating the location of the Chans family heirloom is hidden in three Golden Buddha statues. Paul, an insurance agent, finds one statue by chance and Chans daughter has another one. This makes them targets of treasure-hunting criminals and they have to team up to defeat them before unveiling the hidden secrets.

programme.title: Return of the Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: The Protectors
programme.desc: Ling Hsiao and Kuan Wang Lung are two guard chiefs working for an old convoy master. Lung is secretly in love with Fang Yen, the masters granddaughter but Yen is attracted to Ling Hsiao instead. In order to win her back, Lung sets up a trap to steal the convoy and frames Ling Hsiao for it.

programme.title: Shaolin Martial Arts
programme.desc: The Qing government assigns fighters to destroy Shaolin Temple and kill all the disciples, but two of them successfully escaped. They train under different masters and learn the Wing Chun and Hung Quan styles respectively, finally killing the fighters and taking revenge for the death of their fellow disciples.

programme.title: The Tigress Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Sam is being hunted as he discovers that the mayor and the chief of medical bureau are colluding with a drug dealer. He is saved by a fishermen family and works in their friends grocery but the grocery owner is killed when the enemies track Sam down. Sam escapes to Shaolin to learn the cudgel style of kung fu in order to avenge his friends.

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: Ten Tigers of Kwang Tung
programme.desc: The Ten Tigers of Kwang Tung is a group of anti-Ching martial artists who have killed a Ching official. Years later, when five disciples and descendants of Ten Tigers meet one night, one of them is killed by the son of the late Ching official who returns with a vengeance. They must fight against him to protect the Ten Tigers clan

programme.title: Rolls, Rolls, I Love You
programme.desc: Three young men offend a billionaire and are drawn into a high stakes bet. If they win, they get to keep the billionaires Rolls Royce. Otherwise, they will need to pay the rich man fifty thousand dollars! Will the underdogs win the bet?

programme.title: Finger of Doom
programme.desc: The protagonists are ex-swordmasters who now find joy in making umbrellas. They track down the evil Madame Kung Sun and her poisonous Finger of Doom, a unique supernatural power which allows her to transform normal, everyday people into horrifying zombies, and this is just the start of their mythical adventure against this zombie maker!

programme.title: The Duel of the Century
programme.desc: A duel has been arranged at the Forbidden City between two formidable swordsmen of the martial world, Ye Gu Cheng and Xi Men Chui Xue. Lu Xiao Feng smells something fishy about the duel as the two swordsmen never met and do not have any conflicts. He decides to investigate more with Hua Man Lou, and eventually uncovers some hidden conspiracies

programme.title: The Purple Shell
programme.desc: Hui and Ha are stuck in their unhappy marriages and are attracted to each other when they meet at a party. In one of their beach strolls, Ha picks up a purple shell and gives it to Hui as a memento. When Huis husband finds out about them, he hurts Hui and causes her to become seriously ill, while also blackmails Ha. How will this love story end?

programme.title: Kid From Kwangtung
programme.desc: After many years as a respected actor and action choreographer, the Shaw Studio finally gave the dependable and commendable Hsu Hsia a chance to direct his own movies. He didn't waste the opportunity, inviting three other kung-fu designers to help on this fight-filled thriller. Wang Yu, co-star of such classics as Dirty Ho and The Kid With A Tattoo, here takes center stage as a young rascal caught between an anti-Ching Confederation and violent, vengeful Ching troops. But when he discovers that the good guys are led by master martial arts actor Jen Shih-kuan and the bad guys are led by the incredible Huang Cheng-li everyone knows that loads of great kung-fu is in store.

programme.title: Hex after Hex
programme.desc: Hell may have no fury like a woman scorned, but hell literally, really has no wrath like a lusting ghost scorned! Cult classic director Kuei Chih-hung shoots the works with this amazing horror romance starring muscular "Venom" Lo Meng.

programme.title: Godfather of Canton
programme.desc: A docker, Lin Si Hai, accidentally saves Commissioner Cheng who then offers him a position in the police force. Lin is smart and soon rises through the ranks through treachery and corruption, before becoming a gangster.

programme.title: The House of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: Enchanting Shadow
programme.desc: A young scholar Ning spends the night in a creepy temple that is said to be haunted. He does not believe in the rumours, but soon meets a beautiful female ghost Nie. Nie is forced to stay in the temple to seduce young men for a powerful demon to feast on. Knowing Nie to be a kind ghost, Ning decides to help her escape from the demons clutches.

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household. Qiu Xiang does not believe Bo Hu when he discloses his true identity to her, only falling in love with him when he reveals his talents and with his friends help.

programme.title: Death Duel
programme.desc: Third Master is a renowned swordsman in the martial arts world, but the constant challenges by other swordsmen compel him to fake his death and pursue a secluded life. This does not prevent others from seeking him out to challenge him however, and he is forced to return to fight his way till the end.
